column2: Cerebral Palsy Patient Exercising Cardio Boxing with DS
column3:
Her first time experiencing Cardio Boxing & she's enjoying it!

~Diane Sera~

This is DS Cerebral Palsy patients. She have difficulty moving her limbs due to body muscle weakness. Her weight increased every day because she has given up to move. Here DS going to train her muscles so that one day she could walk normally & being able to lose weight the healthy way.

~Diane Sera~
